an't receive the structural heading bonus (+0.10 is all-caps only).\n    34→- `GREEN BEANS BORKEUM` (all-caps translation on line 1) wins that bonus and outscores the true title.\n    35→- The bilingual suppression logic requires cosine similarity > 0.4 between the two title forms, but Polish ↔ Korean romanization diverges enough in embedding space that the threshold isn't met.\n    36→\n    37→**Common themes:** all-caps structural bias over-powers mixed-case titles; the 3-line join ceiling; \"shorter wins\" dedup mis-firing on OCR fragments; and cross-lingual similarity thresholds being too strict.\n    38→============================================================\n    39→# RAW STREAM (2169 events):\n    40→{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_started\",\"hook_id\":\"6e6ef305-13e9-40a0-a0df-747227eafa3a\",\"hook_name\":\"SessionStart:startup\",\"hook_event\":\"SessionStart\",\"uuid\":\"6f4518ff-bb15-4e5e-ae21-d9d1fecfe718\",\"session_id\":\"a7196b8c-4206-4b90-9bdc-acd6511dfbc5\"}\n    41→{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"hook_response\",\"hook_id\":\"6e6ef305-13e9-40a0-a0df-747227eafa3a\",\"hook_name\":\"SessionStart:startup\",\"hook_event\":\"SessionStart\",\"output\":\"\",\"stdout\":\"\",\"stderr\":\"\",\"exit_code\":0,\"outcome\":\"success\",\"uuid\":\"ef450d65-5f2c-4508-9433-cfa3b806acc4\",\"session_id\":\"a7196b8c-4206-4b90-9bdc-acd6511dfbc5\"}\n    42→{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"init\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola\",\"session_id\":\"a7196b8c-4206-4b90-9bdc-acd6511dfbc5\",\"tools\":[\"Task\",\"TaskOutput\",\"Bash\",\"Glob\",\"Grep\",\"ExitPlanMode\",\"Read\",\"Edit\",\"Write\",\"NotebookEdit\",\"WebFetch\",\"TodoWrite\",\"WebSearch\",\"TaskStop\",\"AskUserQuestion\",\"Skill\",\"EnterPlanMode\",\"EnterWorktree\",\"ExitWorktree\",\"CronCreate\",\"CronDelete\",\"CronList\",\"ToolSearch\",\"ListMcpResourcesTool\",\"ReadMcpResourceTool\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_send_message\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Slack__slack_schedule_message\",\"